<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; font-family: Times;  "><strong>地址：</strong>北海道札幌市中央区南<span style="font-family: Verdana;">5</span>条西<span style="font-family: Verdana;">3</span>丁目</p>
