<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; font-family: Times;  "><strong>交通</strong><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';"><strong>:</strong></span>从<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">JR“</span>札幌<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">”</span>站南出口步行<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">5</span>分钟，地铁<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">“</span>札幌<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">”</span>站<span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';">13</span>号出口</p>
